    },
    {
      "Type": "Paragraph",
      "Content": "Minato only chuckled as he continued his mami, while Anj was clearly enjoying teasing Ryo. Liam was silently eating his own mami, listening at their conversation. There's something about their lightheartedness that made Liam more comfortable with their presence, a sense of comfort and peace that he hadn't experienced for a long, long time, and had yearned. His earlier tension faded away, and the warmth of the atmosphere slowly seeped in again."
    },
    {
      "Type": "Paragraph",
      "Content": "The banter continued between the 3, with Liam listening and eating silently beside them. He was an outsider, still. But he can't deny that their presence brought a warm and welcoming feeling. After a while, the chatter died down into a comfortable silence, the only sound was the bustling food district around them and the pitter patter of the rain from above. After a while, Minato spoke, a warm smile on his face."
