    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Liam",
      "Dialog": "Y-you're welcome...",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Paragraph",
      "Content": "Minato chuckled as he patted Liam's shoulder, which instinctively flinched again."
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Minato",
      "Dialog": "You should stay with us tonight!",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Paragraph",
      "Content": "Ryo's eyes widened as he faced his father, while Anj simply snickered."
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Ryo",
      "Dialog": "Wait, what?",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Minato",
      "Dialog": "What do you say, Liam? Your clothes are all ragged anyway, and the rain is still pouring.",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Ryo",
      "Dialog": "You can't possibly do that dad-",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Minato",
      "Dialog": "Shut up, Ryo. The adult is talking.",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Paragraph",
      "Content": "Ryo grumbled at Minato's dismissal, while Anj chuckled at his predicament. Liam's eyes widened at the elder's offer. It sounded enticing; a shelter from the rain, and a place to rest after months on the run from the organization. He fidgeted with his hands, mulling over the idea, with the thought of them finding out his secret sooner or later if he stayed clashing with the thought of resting easy for tonight."
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Liam",
      "Dialog": "I...",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Paragraph",
      "Content": "His eyes darted between Minato's welcoming gaze and Ryo's disapproving glare. The teenager clearly doesn't want him staying, but he was tired and is in need of rest. He tried not to sound desperate while answering."
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Liam",
      "Dialog": "O-okay...",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Paragraph",
      "Content": "Minato beamed in excitement, while Ryo rolled his eyes at Liam's answer. Despite his disapproval on his father's invitation, he can sense the hint of desperation and exhaustion from Liam's voice. Anj watched the whole thing unfold as she cleans up their empty bowls, preparing to close for the night."
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
