      "Dialog": "Unbelievable.",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Anj",
      "Dialog": "Come on, Ryo. Why are you so against about your father inviting someone over, anyway? I thought you've always wanted a roommate?",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Ryo",
      "Dialog": "Because, <i>Anjerica,</i> the last time dad invited someone over, it turned out to be a gang member trying to break my damn legs.",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Paragraph",
      "Content": "Minato laughed as he recalled that memory."
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Minato",
      "Dialog": "Oh, I remember that! You pushed him out the window like some garbage bag!",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Ryo",
      "Dialog": "Because he <i>is</i> garbage, dad.",
      "Tags": ""
