      "Dialog": "Come on, you think this scruffy kid is in a gang? I highly doubt that.",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Paragraph",
      "Content": "Liam shrinked a little at Anj calling him a \"scruffy\", but he couldn't deny the truth. He looked down at his tattered hoodie he grabbed by the garbage a few weeks ago, and adjusted it to hide the patterns on his body underneath. Ryo, on the other hand, narrows his eyes at Liam, still untrusting even after their dinner."
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Ryo",
      "Dialog": "I know he's not part of the gang, Anj. But he's still an outsider, and a suspicious one at that.",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
