      "Dialog": "Alright! Alright! Enough! Liam's staying with us for the night. That's final.",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Paragraph",
      "Content": "Minato intervened, his voice carrying a sense of finality on his decision. Ryo stopped talking and scoffed, still clearly against a random stranger sleeping at their house. Anj finished cleaning, and was ready to close Minato's stall for the night. Liam sighed in relief as the elderly put a stop at Ryo and Anj's ramblings."
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Minato",
      "Dialog": "Anj, you know what to do, alright? Me, Liam, and Ryo's going home.",
